Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(477,46)}Fabulous
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該有人會從內華達沙漠發現一具身份不明的美少女的屍體了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是小偷嗎  那可是我的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便拿走啊  你這蠢仙人掌！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我  把我的手帕還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,區區仙人掌就想讓我動真格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會後悔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱！我的手燒傷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛  眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會來了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯已經不是我的管家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我成為凪大小姐的管家的第九個月…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經中午了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  已經中午了哦  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊  這麼一大早的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  都說了  已經是中午了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…就算這樣  失去的時間也是回不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真吵啊  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休息日就讓人好好休息嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以都讓您好好地休息到中午了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯這個笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  大小姐  請快換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你是想殺了我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}只是睡到中午起床是不會死的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您好  這裡是三千院家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello? This is Sanzenin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I'm Maria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,And working as a maid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,旋風管家  Can't Take My Eyes Off You
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:34.00,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}罪と罰の雨　降りしくる中　孤独を携え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:41.16,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}縋ることなく　明日を生きると誓え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:45.11,INJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}悪しき邪念に　惑わされても
