Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:23.05,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那へと誘うあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:27.61,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戯れの中で　自由すぎるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:34.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:43.51,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}純真無垢な剣　振り翳す私を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}激しく射抜いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:49.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:51.43,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.99,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使のような　微笑みで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}蜜よりも甘く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:03.37,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}恋の罠　仕掛けてみる（感じて）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:11.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝、今スグ　罪深キ　愛ノ概念ヲ　悔イ改メヨ”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:14.09,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}清らかに導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:19.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる魂　あなたを抱きしめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:14.73,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}Won't you show me all your secrets now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀的心蜷縮在荒漠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:20.19,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀了它的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:23.05,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那間被誘惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:27.61,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺騙的愛中沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:34.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:43.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望揮舞純真無邪之劍的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情地讓疼痛貫穿我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:49.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}Just say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:51.43,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}You know I've got a crush on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.99,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比蜜還甜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:03.37,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}設下愛情的陷阱（感受吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:11.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝那罪惡的愛情觀　現在立刻悔改吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:14.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}純潔地將你引導
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:19.52,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想用純潔的靈魂抱緊你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  各位觀眾感覺這次的「旋風管家」第一夜如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從下回開始劇情也會越來越升溫  各位觀眾…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}小桂～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}啊  死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我怎麼可能就這麼死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}話說我的出場都…
